result:
<!-- 编辑弹框 -->
<a-modal
  title="编辑备注"
  style="top: 20px;"
  :width="600"
  v-model="visible"
  @ok="handleSubmit"
  v-preventReClick
  :destroyOnClose="true"
  :maskClosable="false"
>
  <a-form :form="form">
    <a-form-item label="备注" :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
      <a-textarea
        placeholder="请输入备注"
        :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'remark',
          {
            rules: [{message: '请输入备注' }],
            initialValue: editData.remark,
          }]"
      />
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
